and a better apartment and the American cultural dream in the 80s.

30:42.000 --> 30:47.000
I went and got my masters at the University of Chicago, and I went to work on Wall Street

30:47.000 --> 30:50.000
and I managed money for billionaires effectively.

30:50.000 --> 30:58.000
I had to cold call people, but I wasn't allowed to call anyone if they were worth less than $100 million.

30:58.000 --> 31:01.000
I'm serious. This was 1993.

31:02.000 --> 31:10.000
