31:34.000 --> 31:37.000
Oh my God, it's incredibly powerful.

31:37.000 --> 31:42.000
I never heard the word energy mention my entire master's program in finance.

31:42.000 --> 31:47.000
What? We don't pay for any of the pollution and the externalities.

31:47.000 --> 31:50.000
Those aren't included in the prices.

31:50.000 --> 32:00.000
