35:07.000 --> 35:14.000
and I talked to retired politicians above 70 years old who had time to learn about these things.

35:14.000 --> 35:24.000
And then two years ago, just about now, I started this podcast and I've learned a ton

35:24.000 --> 35:31.000
and I'll echo what you just said a few minutes ago that I have a pretty strong opinion

35:31.000 --> 35:41.000
about how the world works and where we're headed, but I also know that no one can know everything

35:41.000 --> 35:46.000
and there's so many things that I learned from all of my conversations.

35:46.000 --> 35:52.000
