35:52.000 --> 36:02.000
but not only facts, also the humanity of people and how everyone on this program that I've hosted

36:02.000 --> 36:08.000
really cares about the future and not a lot of us have answers on what to do,

36:08.000 --> 36:15.000
but I think there's this emergence of this intellectual, heart-led understanding

36:15.000 --> 36:22.000
and hope for a better future that there's something building there that I think is potentially important.

36:22.000 --> 36:31.000
Right. And then on that journey from, say, working with those multi-millionaires to now,

36:31.000 --> 36:35.000
just to keep you could name one big cognitive shift that you've made,

36:35.000 --> 36:43.000
one big emotional change that you've made in your life and practical changes about where and how you live.

36:43.000 --> 36:51.000
A big cognitive change. The cognitive change is the superorganism is incredibly powerful

36:51.000 --> 36:58.000
and 15 years ago, I wouldn't have imagined that on the dawn of 2024,

36:58.000 --> 37:03.000
we would still have this amount of debt and this amount of energy.

37:03.000 --> 37:16.000
