37:16.000 --> 37:23.000
So I've cognitively come to respect that, though at the same time, the more it grows and expands,

37:23.000 --> 37:30.000
the worse the biosphere and other species are generally.

37:30.000 --> 37:44.000
Emotionally, well, I've grieved for the future that our society tells us is coming long ago.

37:45.000 --> 37:51.000
So my expectations are lower than the average person.

37:51.000 --> 37:54.000
So emotionally, I've come to terms with that.

37:57.000 --> 38:02.000
